0.9.14a (23-NOV-2008)
--------------------------------------
* Minor bug fixed in utils/fs.h. When appending a char for std::string should use push_back method

0.9.8a (23-MAR-2008)
--------------------------------------
* fixed bug for memory leak
* Change the find the attribute function, abondoned the map.find() function which could not find the last element


0.9.8 (21-MAR-2008)
--------------------------------------
* adding the features for installation of stpl in Makefile.am configure.ac under the source root path
* making it simpler and easier to parse html or xml file, use a single parser and return a parsed tree like dom


0.9.7a (13-MAR-2008)
--------------------------------------
* Add a function for transform different charset to another


0.9.7 (09-MAR-2008)
--------------------------------------
* made the parser be able to gererate a node tree, and getting the specific attribute for certain tag


0.9.6a (08-MAR-2008)
--------------------------------------
* minor change on the html element tag class, with regarding to where to stop for the element with a optional end tag


0.9.6 (06-MAR-2008)
